<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Why Royal Holiday Homes</title>

  <!-- Geist Font -->
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Geist:wght@100..900&family=Noto+Sans:ital,wght@0,100..900;1,100..900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

  <style>
    body {
      background: #f2f2f2;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      font-family: 'Geist', system-ui, sans-serif;
    }

    /* A4 Page */
    .a4-page {
      width: 491px;
      height: 694px;
      background: #ffffff;
      padding: 20px;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      position: relative;
    }

    /* Inner bordered area */
    .inner-div {
      width: 451px;
      height: 654px;
      border: 2px solid #caa46a;
      padding: 20px;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      position: relative;
    }

    /* Corner Logo */
    .corner-logo {
      width: 14px;
      position: absolute;
      top: 18px;
      right: 18px;
    }

    /* Title */
    .title {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #7A542A;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .subtitle {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 10px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    /* Points Wrapper */
    .points {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    /* Single Point */
    .point {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    /* Black Diamond */
    .diamond {
      width: 20px;
      height: 20px;
      background: black;
      transform: rotate(45deg);
      margin-top: 2px;
    }

    /* Content */
    .content {
      flex: 1;
    }

    /* Gold Arrow Heading */
    .heading {
      background: #EFCE8D;
      font-size: 10px;
      font-weight: 600;
      padding: 6px 15px;
      clip-path: polygon(0 0, 95% 0, 100% 50%, 95% 100%, 0 100%, 3% 50%);
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    /* Paragraph */
    .content p {
      font-size: 10px;
      font-weight: 400;
      line-height: 1.5;
      margin: 0;
    }

    /* Footer */
    .footer {
      font-size: 10px;
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 5px;
      left: 20px;
      color: #777;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <div class="a4-page">
    <div class="inner-div">

      <!-- Corner Logo -->
      <img src="/images/R.svg" class="corner-logo" alt="Royal Logo">

      <!-- Title -->
      <h1 class="title">WHY ROYAL HOLIDAY HOMES?</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">We are Operators, Not Just Agents.</p>

      <!-- Points List -->
      <div class="points">

        <div class="point">
          <div class="diamond"></div>
          <div class="content">
            <div class="heading">ABU DHABI SPECIALISTS</div>
            <p>Deep local knowledge of building regulations and guest preferences.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="point">
          <div class="diamond"></div>
          <div class="content">
            <div class="heading">EARN MORE</div>
            <p>We offer a supportive environment where you can grow your business and earn more profit and our helpful support team is always here to assist you.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="point">
          <div class="diamond"></div>
          <div class="content">
            <div class="heading">IN-HOUSE TEAMS</div>
            <p>Our cleaning, maintenance, and laundry are not outsourced.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="point">
          <div class="diamond"></div>
          <div class="content">
            <div class="heading">PROVEN COMPLIANCE</div>
            <p>Fully licensed by the Department of Culture and Tourism.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="point">
          <div class="diamond"></div>
          <div class="content">
            <div class="heading">PERFORMANCE FIRST</div>
            <p>Our goals are aligned—we only earn when you earn.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="point">
          <div class="diamond"></div>
          <div class="content">
            <div class="heading">HASSLE FREE</div>
            <p>We're always committed to making your experience and living smooth, hassle-free, comfortable, and enjoyable as possible.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="point">
          <div class="diamond"></div>
          <div class="content">
            <div class="heading">VALUE FOR MONEY</div>
            <p>Our pricing is transparent, so you can trust that you're getting a reliable deal. We constantly evaluate our offerings to ensure that we are delivering real value.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">Confidential © Royal Holiday Homes</div>
  </div>

</body>
</html>
